position: 204,-140
---
Detective: Who are you, exactly?
Butterbur: Dale Butterbur, I own this bar. It was used by bootleggers during the prohibition, would you believe, but the old owner went to the big house for brewing his own hooch, and viola, it was mine for the buying, right as the prohibition ended.

