title: Loretta
position: 171,192
---
Detective: What do you know about Loretta Dubois?
Butterbur: She performs here once a week - she’s a great singer. Obviously she’s a bit of a dish too, which brings in the customers. I think Harlow got it for her bad. Never missed a performance. He was more likely to pay her just for existing than me was to pay me for booze.

